	dprr:hasNoteText "2 It has been supposed that Globulus is the governor of Asia mentioned in Joseph. AJ 14.244-246 (cf. SIG³ 720, note 3), but this is possible only if # in the text is a mistake for Globulus and # represents Propraetor." .
